===Noun===
'''[[jarbua]] [[terapon]]'''
# An [[edible]] [[omnivorous]] [[fish]], [[fawn]] in color on top, [[cream]]-colored below, with a dark [[nape]], and three or four curved dark brown bands run from the nape to the hind part of the body, the lowermost continuing across the middle of the [[caudal fin]], scientific name ''Terapon jarbua'' of the ''[[Actinopterygii]]'' [[order]].

====Synonyms====
*[[crescent perch]]
*[[crescent-banded grunter]]
*[[Crescent-banded tiger-fish]]
*[[crescent grunter]]
*[[jarbua]] (Cambodia)
*[[squeaking perch]]
*[[thornfish]] (African term)
*[[threestripe tigerfish]]
*[[tiger-perch]]

